# Web Development Icons

#### The Style Container
```html
<style type="text/css"> </style>
```

#### Common Icon Modifications
```css
.vertical-flip-icon {
  transform: rotate(180deg);
  margin-top: -0.05rem;
}
.size-24{
  width:24px;
  height:24px;
}
.size-48{
  width:48px;
  height:48px;
}
.size-96{
  width:96px;
  height:96px;
}
```
